@startuml US_3.1.3_SSD
autonumber

actor "System\nUser" as User
participant ":System" as System

== Login ==
activate User
User -> System: Clica em "Login"
activate System
System --> User: Apresenta formulário de login
deactivate System
User -> System: Introduz credenciais e submete
activate System
System --> User: devolve sessão autenticada
deactivate System

== View Menu ==
User -> System: Acede ao menu principal
activate System
System --> User: Apresenta menu baseado no perfil do utilizador
deactivate System

== Attempt Unauthorized Access ==
User -> System: Tenta aceder a funcionalidade restrita
activate System
System --> User: devolve mensagem de acesso negado
deactivate System
deactivate User

@enduml
